news_header: Keith Kellogg, Special Ambassador, arrives in Kiev to meet Ukrainian leadership amid unclear role in peace talks.
news_original_title: Trumpin erityislähettiläs Keith Kellogg on Kiovassa
news_text: Keith Kellogg, Special Ambassador to President Trump, has arrived in Kiev to meet with President Zelensky and other Ukrainian leaders. His role in peace talks remains unclear, as he missed a meeting between Russian and US foreign ministers. Russia claims he is part of the US negotiating team, but the US has not confirmed this.
